    <tu tuid="shijing__xiaoya-yuzao-009__001__zhwikisource-20260530__legge-sbe-v3-1879">
      <prop type="x-section-id">xiaoya-yuzao-009</prop>
      <prop type="x-alignment-type">exact_or_near_exact</prop>
      <prop type="x-confidence">0.99</prop>
      <prop type="x-chinese-ref">詩經·小雅·魚藻之什·009.1</prop>
      <prop type="x-translation-ref">白華.1</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>白華菅兮，白茅束兮。之子之遠，俾我獨兮。
英英白雲，露彼菅茅。天步艱難，之子不猶。
滮池北流，浸彼稻田。嘯歌傷懷，念彼碩人。
樵彼桑薪，卬烘于煁。維彼碩人，實勞我心。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>The fibres from the white-flowered rush
Are bound with the white grass.
This man's sending me away
makes me dwell solitary.</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
    <tu tuid="shijing__xiaoya-yuzao-009__002__zhwikisource-20260530__legge-sbe-v3-1879">
      <prop type="x-section-id">xiaoya-yuzao-009</prop>
      <prop type="x-alignment-type">exact_or_near_exact</prop>
      <prop type="x-confidence">0.99</prop>
      <prop type="x-chinese-ref">詩經·小雅·魚藻之什·009.2</prop>
      <prop type="x-translation-ref">白華.2</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>鼓鍾于宮，聲聞于外。念子懆懆，視我邁邁。
有鶖在梁，有鶴在林。維彼碩人，實勞我心。
鴛鴦在梁，戢其左翼。之子無良，二三其德。
有扁斯石，履之卑兮。之子之遠，俾我疧兮。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>The light and brilliant clouds
Bedew the rush and the grass.
The way of Heaven is hard and difficult;—
This
man does not conform (to good principle).</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
